     <profileDesc>
        <abstract><p>The officials of district (pargana) <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, division (sarkar) <placeName ref="#mandu">Mandu</placeName>, province (suba) <placeName ref="#malwa">Malwa</placeName> are notified that based on his good performance, the landlord (chaudhri) <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> has been granted a village in perpetuity for the support of himself and his children.</p></abstract>       
