  <text>
      <body>
         
         <pb n="1r" facs="lf_pDas_1675_dai_lns235ms_h1_r.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div1" xml:lang="per" type="invocation" rend="top centre"><p>ا</p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div1" corresp="#orig_div1"><p>Alif</p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div2" xml:lang="per" type="authorisation" rend="top right"><p><stamp type="seal"><mentioned>
            <persName ref="#islamKhan">اسلام خان</persName>
            بن حسین علی مرید شاه
            <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">عالمگیر</persName>
            <date calendar="#julus">۱۴</date>
            <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">۱۰۸۰</date>
            </mentioned></stamp></p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div2" corresp="#orig_div2">
            <p><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><persName ref="#islamKhan">Islam Khan</persName>, son of Hussein Ali, disciple of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_shah">Shah</ref> <persName ref="#aurangzebAlamgir">Alamgir</persName> <date calendar="#julus">[Regnal Year] 14</date> <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1080</date><note>This seal was issued in 1669–70 CE.</note></mentioned></stamp></p></div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div3" xml:lang="per" type="maintext">
            <p>
               <lb/>متصدیان مهمات حال و استقبال پرگنه
               <placeName ref="#pgDhar">دهار</placeName>
               سرکار
               <placeName ref="#mandu">مندو</placeName>
               صوبه
               <placeName ref="#malwa">مالوا</placeName>
               بدانند که
               <lb/>دریولا حقیقت دولتخواهی و نیکو خدمتی و آبادانکاری
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">پرسوتم داس</persName>
               چودهری
               <lb/>بعرض رسد که در سرانجام مهام آنجا مساعی جمله بظهور میرساند بنابران موضع
               <placeName ref="#kusawada">کساودها</placeName>
               <lb/>عمله پرگنه مذکور در وجه انعام و نانکار مشارالیه با فرزندان بدستور سابق مقرر فرمودیم
               <lb/>باید که موضه مسطور را بموجب حسب الضمن از ابتدای فصلخریف
               <date calendar="#turkish">توشقان ایل</date>
               سنه
               <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">۱۰۸۳</date>
               بتصرف
               <lb/>مشارالیه واگذارند که حاصلات آنرا سال بسال صرف
               مایحتاج
               خود نموده
               <lb/>در تقدیم مراسم خیرات دولتخواهی مقدور کرم باشد 
               <app><rdg cert="medium">عن</rdg><rdg cert="low">تحریر</rdg></app>
               <date calendar="#julus">
               غره رمضان سنه
               <num>۱۹</num></date>
               <g ref="#baiz">بیض</g>
            </p>    
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div3" corresp="#orig_div3">
            <p>
               <lb/>The important officials of the present and future of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_sarkar">sarkar</ref> <placeName ref="#mandu">Mandu</placeName>, <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_suba">suba</ref> <placeName ref="#mandu">Malwa</placeName> should know that 
               <lb/>at this time, the facts about the loyalty and good service and efforts to populate [the area] by the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_chaudhri">chaudhri</ref> <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName> 
               <lb/>have been brought to attention and [the fact] that he makes efforts to complete the important tasks there is evident. On that basis, the village of <placeName ref="#kusawada">Kusawadha</placeName> 
               <lb/>in the administration of the said <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_pargana">pargana</ref> is given as <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_inam">inʿam</ref> and <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_nankar">nankar</ref> to the said person along with his descendants, as per past practice.  
               <lb/>The said village, according to the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_zimn">zimn</ref>, must be given into the possession of the said person from the beginning of the season of <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_kharif">kharif</ref> of the <date calendar="#turkish">hare year</date>, year <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1083</date>,   
               <lb/>so that the collections from therein year to year should be used for his expenses, 
               <lb/>[and] he should be engaged generously in the promotion of the good works of loyalty. On the first night of the new moon of Ramzan in the year <date calendar="#julus">19</date>. <g ref="#baiz">Ended</g>.
            </p>   
         </div>
         
         <pb n="1v" facs="lf_pDas_1675_dai_lns235ms_h1_v.jpg"/>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div4" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="bottom right">
            <p>
               <lb/><stamp type="seal"><mentioned><gap/>
                  <persName ref="#muhammadAmin">محمد امین</persName>
                  بنده
                  <persName ref="#islamKhan">اسلام خان</persName>
                  <date>۱۰۸۴</date>
                  </mentioned></stamp>
               <lb/>فی التاریخ
               <lb/>غره رمضان
               <lb/> سنه
               <num>۱۹</num> <gap/>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div4" corresp="#orig_div4">
            <p><lb/><stamp type="seal">Round black ink seal<mentioned><gap/>
               <persName ref="#muhammadAmin">Muhammad Amin</persName>, servant of 
               <persName ref="#islamKhan">Islam Khan</persName> [in the] year <date calendar="#hijri-qamri">1084</date><note>This seal was issued in 1673–74 CE.</note></mentioned></stamp>
               <lb/>On the date of
               <lb/>the first night of the new moon of Ramzan
               <lb/> year 19 <gap/>
            </p>      
         </div>
         
         <div xml:id="orig_div5" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="middle right"><p>ضمن نویسی
         </p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div5" corresp="#orig_div5"><p>The writing of the <ref type="glossary" target="#gl_zimn">zimn</ref>
         </p></div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div6" xml:lang="per" type="clericalNotes" rend="top right"><p><unclear>قلم نماید</unclear></p></div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div6" corresp="#orig_div6"><p><unclear>It was written.</unclear></p></div>
         <div xml:id="orig_div7" xml:lang="per" type="laterAddition" rend="top centre">
            <p>نمبر 
               <num>۲</num></p>
         </div>
         <div xml:id="trans_div7" corresp="#orig_div7">
            <p>Number 2</p>
         </div>
      </body>
